data.description: * OWNER FINANCING *  Welcome to beautiful South Philly! This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home has been remodeled and includes high end hardwood laminate flooring, fresh paint, and updated kitchen and baths. Home includes washer/dryer, all appliances - dishwasher, oven/stove, garbage disposal, and refrigerator.  Radiator hot water heating in the colder months brings the best source of heat. A cozy outdoor backyard patio will be fun to frequent in the warmer months!
